Read about the cupcake ATM and decided that I needed to try it. Cupcake was OK but not what I expected for almost $5. This was my first Sprinkles cupcake and I know they are pretty much responsible for the gourmet cupcake trend but I've had better. Sweet Daddy Cupcakes are about twice the size for the same price and unlike this cupcake were moist. Won't go back again.

