One of the better Burger's you can get at a chain. I've had Five Guys Burger's in 3 different states and a half dozen different establishments. Burgers are made to order with unlimited toppings. The regular size burger and cheeseburger are both double patties, in most cases a single works fine for me. As good as the burgers are the fries. They pack them in and overflow into the bag, well seasoned.

